V0105_01_00_00_0.text:
Heh. You want to Duel me? 
This will be entertaining... and short!

V0105_01_00_01_0.text: I'll always triumph because I'm the Chazz!

V0105_01_00_01_1.text: And I'm gonna Chazz you up!

V0105_01_00_02_0.text:
Let's Duel, Jaden!
There's no way a Slifer slacker will defeat me!

V0105_01_00_03_0.text:
Alexis, my Alexis...
You don't realize you love me yet.

V0105_01_00_03_1.text: But when I defeat you in a Duel, you will!

V0105_01_00_04_0.text:
Aster? More like "laster"!
You stand no chance against the Chazz!

V0105_01_00_05_0.text: You have six different Decks to beat me with? Lies!

V0105_01_00_05_1.text: There are zero Decks that can defeat me!

V0105_03_00_00_0.text: Stop wasting my time and give up already!

V0105_03_00_01_0.text: Your moves are putting me to sleep!

V0105_03_00_04_0.text: Looks like you have a tinsy winsy bit of skill.

V0105_03_00_05_0.text: You really wanna make me angry, huh?

V0105_05_00_00_0.text: No one defeats the Chazz! No one!

V0105_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0105_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Magical Mallet!

V0105_08_00_01_0.text:
My Continuous Spell activates!
Frontline Base!

V0105_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Inferno Reckless Summon!

V0105_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Chthonian Alliance!

V0105_08_00_04_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Inferno Tempest!

V0105_08_00_04_1.text:
You think you know my strategies?
Then I'll banish 'em!

V0105_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Return from the Different Dimension!

V0105_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
The Graveyard in the Fourth Dimension!

V0105_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
The Grave of Enkindling!

V0105_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Level Up!!

V0105_08_00_09_0.text: Good bros support each other, even if they're the weakest of the weak!

V0105_08_00_09_1.text:
Put your puny powers to use!
Ojama Delta Hurricane!!!!

V0105_08_00_10_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Enchanting Fitting Room!

V0105_08_00_11_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Level Modulation!

V0105_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Ojama Trio!

V0105_08_00_12_1.text: I Special Summon 3 Ojama Tokens on your field!

V0105_08_00_13_0.text: Luck is still on my side.

V0105_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Ojamuscle!

V0105_08_00_14_1.text: You've served your purpose, Ojamas! Bye bye!

V0105_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Level Down!?

V0105_08_00_16_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Armed Changer!

V0105_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Chaos End!

V0105_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Lightning Vortex!

V0105_08_00_21_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Chthonian Polymer!

V0105_08_00_22_0.text: I activate my Equip Spell, Megamorph!

V0105_08_00_23_0.text:
My Continuous Trap activates!
Final Attack Orders!

V0105_08_00_24_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, A Feather of the Phoenix!

V0105_08_00_25_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Ring of Defense!

V0105_08_00_26_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Treasure Map!

V0105_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dragonic Tactics!

V0105_08_00_29_0.text: This will make my weaklings just a bit more useful... maybe.

V0105_08_00_29_1.text: I activate the Field Spell, Ojama Country!

V0105_08_00_30_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Pride Shout!

V0105_08_00_30_1.text: When a monster with 0 ATK attacks directly, you take damage equal to its DEF!

V0105_08_00_31_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Thanks for the help so far!

V0105_08_00_31_1.text:
But your time's up!
Thunder Crash!

V0105_08_00_32_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Dark Mambele!

V0105_09_00_08_0.text: Armed Dragon LV3 activates its effect!

V0105_09_00_08_1.text: I Special Summon Armed Dragon LV5!

V0105_09_00_10_0.text: Armed Dragon LV7, activate your effect!

V0105_09_00_18_1.text: Bring your grandparents for a visit!

V0105_09_00_19_0.text: Mefist the Infernal General, show 'em what you can do!

V0105_09_00_20_1.text: You also take the damage that I took!

V0105_09_00_21_0.text: Light and Darkness Dragon's effect activates!

V0105_09_00_23_0.text: I activate Dark End Dragon's effect!

V0105_09_00_26_0.text: I activate Dark Armed Dragon's effect!

V0105_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0105_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0105_13_00_01_0.text: Feast your eyes on W-Wing Catapult!

V0105_13_00_02_0.text:
Start your engines and merge! 
VW-Tiger Catapult!

V0105_13_00_04_0.text: Y-Dragon Head is ready to rock!

V0105_13_00_06_0.text: I combine X, Y and Z into XYZ-Dragon Cannon!

V0105_13_00_12_0.text: Join me in welcoming Armed Dragon LV7!

V0105_13_00_13_0.text:
Hahaha!
Here comes my all-powerful Armed Dragon LV10!

V0105_13_00_21_0.text: Here comes Mefist the Infernal General!

V0105_13_00_23_0.text: Will you fight alongside me again?

V0105_13_00_25_0.text: Emerge from the depths of darkness!

V0105_13_00_26_0.text: Shine your light in the darkness!

V0105_14_00_01_0.text: You're not ready for this! Battle!

V0105_15_00_02_0.text: I have no time for chumps!

V0105_16_00_00_0.text: Get ready to get knocked down!

V0105_19_00_00_0.text: V-Tiger Jet! Sharpen your claws and attack!

V0105_19_00_07_1.text:
Go, VWXYZ-Dragon Catapult Cannon!
Ultimate Destruction!

V0105_19_00_14_1.text: Because you're the ace in my Deck! No foolin'!

V0105_19_00_17_0.text: Hurry up and attack, Ojama Red!

V0105_21_00_02_0.text: You'll pay! I end my turn!

V0105_28_00_00_0.text: I'm the Chazz, and don't you forget it!

V0105_28_00_00_1.text:
Chazz it up!
Chazz it up!

V0105_28_00_01_0.text: Maybe you were somebody back home, but here in the big leagues, you’re nothing but a pathetic little amateur.

V0105_28_00_02_0.text: Even the weakest cards become powerful, as long as I'm the one wielding them!

V0105_28_00_03_0.text: You're dumber than I thought, and that's saying a lot!

V0105_28_00_04_0.text: Alexis, now that we're a couple...

V0105_28_00_05_0.text: The Chazz doesn't know the meaning of defeat!

V0105_28_00_05_1.text: But you sure do, Laster Phoenix!

V0105_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh...
Dumb luck. That's all it was!

V0105_29_00_01_1.text: And the Chazz never stays down for long!

V0105_29_00_02_0.text:
Cough cough...
I would've won if I didn't have this cold.

V0105_29_00_02_1.text: I'll let you off this time.

V0105_29_00_03_0.text:
Argh!
Why can't I defeat this slacker?!?

V0105_29_00_04_0.text:
My skill's broken...
My heart's broken too...
Sigh...

V0105_29_00_05_0.text:
Grr...
The Chazz is no loser!

V0105_30_00_00_0.text:
Hahaha!
No Duelist can beat me, no matter what cards you have!

V0105_30_00_01_0.text: Your lousy monsters won’t get you out of this jam!

V0105_33_00_01_0.text: Even the weak have their uses!

V0105_33_00_02_0.text: You're about to learn the hard way - the Chazz way!

V0105_34_00_00_0.text: Argh! Stop bugging me, Ojamas! We are not BFF's!

V0105_34_00_02_0.text: The Ojamas taught me that when I think I met the biggest loser, there's always a bigger loser waiting!

V0105_34_00_04_0.text:
You want me to go easy? Ha!
I love being the thorn in your side!

V0105_34_00_05_0.text: You can never understand the heights I strive for because you're not elite like me!

V0105_34_00_06_0.text: You had no idea what you were getting into!

V0105_34_00_07_0.text:
I'll do things my way!
The Chazz way!

V0105_34_00_08_0.text:
Chazz it up!
Chazz it up!

V0105_35_00_01_0.text: The Chazz is on the job!
